      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Sequence\n\n## Phase 1\n- define the nodeset skill contract\n- map the planning nodeset into it\n- decide repair authority boundaries\n\n## Phase 2\n- implement validation and drift detection\n- wire reports to concrete graph-local output\n- test on real planning graphs\n\n## Phase 3\n- implement bounded repair workflows\n- normalize contract and archive issues\n- keep humans in the review loop\n\n## Phase 4\n- document the reusable pattern\n- separate planning-specific rules from generic ones\n- extend the approach to future nodesets",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
